# Vagrantfile
#   Provisions an Oracle FPP (Fleet Patching and Provisioning) lab with
#   Oracle Database 19c (19.3.0) Grid Infrastructure on Oracle Linux 7.
#
#   Supports both VirtualBox and KVM/libvirt providers. Single-node FPP cluster
#   (host1 + host2) or single-node FPP cluster (set host2.deploy: 'false').
#
#   Author: Ruggero Citton <ruggero.citton@oracle.com>
#           RAC Pack, Cloud Innovation and Solution Engineering Team
